<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that moved substantially or traded  
heavily Wednesday on the New York Stock Exchange, Nasdaq Stock 
Market, and American Stock Exchange. 

</P>
<P>
 *NYSE    	

</P>
<P>
 *IBM rose 15 1/16 to 236 1/4    	
</P>
<P>
	After shares of Big Blue dropped in recent sessions, investors  
are returning to buy the widely held stock at a more affordable 
price. It will become ``cheaper'' yet again after the close of 
trading, when a 2-for-1 stock split takes effect. 

</P>
<P>
 *DLJ Direct, priced at 20, rose to 30    	
</P>
<P>
