 *NASDAQ   	

</P>
<P>
 *Visx fell 5 3/8 to 50    	
</P>
<P>
	The Wall Street Journal reported in Wednesday's edition that  
Visx faces federal actions and litigation over patents for its 
laser eye surgery. A number of competing companies are also 
beginning to perform the surgery, intended to correct 
nearsightedness. 

</P>
