20th century was to be selected tonight among the 10 finalists 
chosen from 83 contestants. The finalists were from Botswana, 
Ghana, India, Jamaica, Mexico, Philippines, Puerto Rico, South 
Africa, Spain and Venezuela. The contest on CBS-TV was broadcast 
live to 80 countries. 

