<CATEGORY> financial </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> The Lighter Side of Business /  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *AP Corrects Watercooler Item    	
</P>
<P>
	In a May 25 Watercooler business column, The Associated Press  
erroneously reported that a survey on children who care for their 
elderly parents was done by the employment consulting firm 
Challenger, Gray &AMP; Christmas. 
</P>
<P>
	The survey was done by SCAN, a California non-profit managed  
health care plan for seniors. 
</P>
</TEXT>
